<a href="/wiki/Western_Massachusetts" title="Western Massachusetts">Western Massachusetts</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Location</th><td class="infobox-data label"><a href="/wiki/Windsor_Locks,_Connecticut" title="Windsor Locks, Connecticut">Windsor Locks, Connecticut</a>, U.S.</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Operating base for</th><td class="infobox-data"><a href="/wiki/Breeze_Airways" title="Breeze Airways">Breeze Airways</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label"><a href="/wiki/Time_zone" title="Time zone">Time zone</a></th><td class="infobox-data">EST (-5)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Elevation&#160;<a href="/wiki/Height_above_sea_level" class="mw-redirect" title="Height above sea level">AMSL</a></th><td class="infobox-data">173&#160;ft / 53&#160;m</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label"><a href="/wiki/Geographic_coordinate_system" title="Geographic coordinate system">Coordinates</a></th><td class="infobox-data"><span class="geo-inline"><span class="plainlinks nourlexpansion load-gadget" data-gadget="WikiMiniAtlas"><a class="external text" href="https://geohack.toolforge.org/geohack.php?pagename=Bradley_International_Airport&amp;params=41_56_21_N_072_41_00_W_region:US-CT_scale:40000_type:airport"><span class="geo-default"><span class="geo-dms" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location"><span class="latitude">41°56′21″N</span> <span class="longitude">072°41′00″W</span></span></span><span class="geo-multi-punct">&#xfeff; / &#xfeff;</span><span class="geo-nondefault"><span class="geo-dec" title="Maps, aerial photos, and other data for this location">41.93917°N 72.68333°W</span><span style="display:none">&#xfeff; / <span class="geo">41.93917; -72.68333</span></span></span></a></span></span></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" class="infobox-label">Website</th><td class="infobox-data plainlinksneverexpand"><span class="url"><a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href